long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The sole purpose of this extension is to hide the intellisyntax/autocomplete feature of Qlik Sense Data Load Editor. It should fire a simple css snippet on pages matching *dataloadeditor* or *sense/app*. Please report any bugs or side-effects.
